title: Egg Muffins
directions: Lightly coat 12 cup muffin pan with spray
Place eggs in large bowl; whisk to blend. Season with salt and pepper if desired.
Add spinach, bell pepper and onions; mix well.
Evenly pour egg mixture into the muffin cups.
Bake for 20 minutes, or until toothpick is inserted comes out clean
*You can add goat cheese, feta cheese, mozzarrella cheese, cheddar or Parmesan.
ingredients: 1 (10 oz) bag of finely chopped spinach
sea salt, black pepper, and onion to taste
